uces the overfitting issue,\nenabling us to deepen the model up to 13 layers (from 9) without compromising\nthe accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 01:09:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-08"}
