 dust SED occurs between redshifts $z\\sim 3$ and 2\nin the progenitors of the simulated MW-like galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 07:56:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-20"}
