ections, where both mobile lid and optimal\ntidal heating could be sustained on eccentric (e>0.1) Earth-sized exoplanets\n(${R}_{p}$ = 1.0-1.23R$_\\oplus$) orbiting in the CHZ of low-mass M dwarfs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2022 15:14:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-08"}
